description: On this in-studio episode of The CouRage & Nadeshot Show, BasicallyIDoWrk (Marcel) & Symfuhny (Mason) come on the show to talk about working with VanossGaming & Wildcat, strip club encounters in GTA, burnout from playing Among Us, COD Cold War, NBA Draft, XQC's 7-Day ban, and how Marcel pranked Ninja on their first meeting in person. Nadeshot and CouRage also open up the 100 Thieves 1 Million Subscriber YouTube Button!
